{"tid":2122481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港有船員確診    海事處證逾萬名船員獲豁免檢疫","createTime":"2020-07-24T04:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90f43fab4278f54f6100b7626370c7004bd1ebda","tid":2122481,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/本港有船員確診-海事處證逾萬名船員獲豁免檢疫-031700474.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E6%9C%89%E8%88%B9%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%8B%E8%99%95%E8%AD%89%E9%80%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E8%88%B9%E5%93%A1%E7%8D%B2%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB-031700474.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6P3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=98158e11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/本港有船員確診-海事處證逾萬名船員獲豁免檢疫-031700474.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZHS3V9qHgrGbY.tFi8DJHA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200724a112306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZHS3V9qHgrGbY.tFi8DJHA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200724a112306.jpg&h=73d16e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】本港近日出現船員確診個案。海事處證實，現時已有超過一萬名船員獲豁免強制檢疫，當中包括在香港國際機場海天客運碼頭提供轉駁服務的快船船員。不過處方表示，有向獲豁免船員及其公司或代理實施一系列特定條件及措施，以減低公共衞生風險。<br />\n<br />\n海事處指，曾徵詢食物及衞生局與衞生署，有關人士須遵守一系列特定條件及措施，包括在離開出發地前的48小時內接受核酸測試，並取得呈陰性的檢測結果；船員到港後，其公司或代理亦需安排住宿供其自我隔離，直至下一次登船為止，而衞生署亦會要求船員於留港期間進行14日醫學監察，並要戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，以及向衞生署呈報任何不適。另外，為減低船員與社區的接觸，有關船隻只會停靠貨櫃碼頭或錨地等，讓船員上落，而非靠泊其他地方如郵輪碼頭。"},{"pid":"b71fd9122bfbcf8190e05a86aecc2a05dc85a27f","tid":2122481,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"真係全地球專家嚟哂香港都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70638128d556676b5e5e8be67347fd5c860bd669","tid":2122481,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a6a7c9c000d4c1711c204d111b375817a5501f","tid":2122481,"uid":85552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"其實係突登等多啲人中招<br />\n然後請大陸醫護落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abbdc575a45d43bc59fd82e4c1c97d6b701ac013","tid":2122481,"uid":118120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:38:40.000Z","msg":"港共先係搞攬炒果個"},{"pid":"e18ee532a522268b7ed9d53c32865be9985dc890","tid":2122481,"uid":334765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母真係唔係浪得虛名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf7ea3f449b482e7f2e3accbf43c9fb167668e","tid":2122481,"uid":156130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36a6a7c9c000d4c1711c204d111b375817a5501f","tid":2122481,"uid":85552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:35:16.000Z","msg":"其實係突登等多啲人中招<br />\n然後請大陸醫護落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:46:10.000Z","msg":"同埋嚇死你<br />\n要你完全接受高壓統治<br />\n<br />\n其實又唔係咩世紀絕症<br />\n傷風感冒一日都唔止一百宗啦<br />\n先搞到個病好似好恐怖咁<br />\n再嚇死你冇得唔跟政惡法"}]}